room_title: Escape room "The Museum" by Escape Games Worcester in Worcester
room_description: Long ago, this beautiful museum was a secret meeting place for a covert organization. What nefarious deeds were they planning? What clues have been hidden for us to find centuries later? You may have dug too deep because the doors have locked you in... There must be something they don’t want the outside world to know. You’ll have to use cryptology and ingenuity to find out what happened in this very room!
